%main.single-main
  %section.l-single-container
    %h2.l-chapter-head.registration 電話番号認証
    %form.l-single-inner.registration-form{:action => "https://www.mercari.com/jp/signup/address/", :method => "POST", :novalidate => "novalidate"}
      %input{:name => "after_save_callback", :type => "hidden", :value => ""}/
      .l-single-content
        .form-group
          %label{:for => "captcha"} 認証番号
          %input.input-default{:name => "captcha", :placeholder => "認証番号を入力", :type => "number", :value => ""}/
        %p.l-single-text SMSで届いた認証番号を入力してください
        %button.btn-default.btn-red{:type => "submit"} 認証して完了
      %input{:name => "__csrf_value", :type => "hidden", :value => "29877392f8ba8e6847a1ecaeb819a91eb2ef9819ba6446d7bc06042a92a3e40e7b660081f2d72e2ec6ea1952cc9a32f03d5a4fcd6e8244f8d2487802cccb178ef"}/
      %input{:name => "id", :type => "hidden", :value => "894807894"}/
    %form.l-single-inner.registration-form{:action => "https://www.mercari.com/jp/signup/sms_confirmation/phone/", :method => "POST", :novalidate => "novalidate"}
      %input{:name => "after_save_callback", :type => "hidden", :value => ""}/
      .l-single-content
        %h3.l-chapter-sub-head 30秒たっても認証番号が届かない方へ
        %p.l-single-text 電話で認証番号を聞くこともできます。
        %button.btn-default.btn-red{:type => "submit"} 電話で認証番号を聞く（通話無料）
      %input{:name => "__csrf_value", :type => "hidden", :value => "29877392f8ba8e6847a1ecaeb819a91eb2ef9819ba6446d7bc06042a92a3e40e7b660081f2d72e2ec6ea1952cc9a32f03d5a4fcd6e8244f8d2487802cccb178ef"}/
      %input{:name => "id", :type => "hidden", :value => "894807894"}/
    .l-single-inner.registration-form
      .l-single-content
        %h3.l-chapter-sub-head 認証番号を再送することもできます。もう一度電話番号を入力して下さい。
        %p
          %a{:href => "/jp/signup/sms_confirmation/"} 電話番号を再度入力する
        %p.l-single-text
          ※SMSが届かない場合は
          %a{:href => "/jp/help_center/article/248/", :target => "_blank"}> SMS受信設定
          を確認して、もう一度電話番号を入力してください。
